com.github.naoghuman.lib.preferences.core

Interface PreferencesFactory.ThirdStep

  • Enclosing class:
    PreferencesFactory

    public static interface PreferencesFactory.ThirdStep
    The last step in this factory. In this step the developer can access or put the value through the defined key from the previous step.

    In all get(T) methods the default value will returned if the key isn't found.
    In all put(T) methods the given value will be stored associated with the key in the previous choosen scope (application / module).

    Since:
    0.6.0
    Version:
    0.6.0
    Author:
    Naoghuman
